
Selenium WebDriver
=====================
-Selenium WebDriver is an interface
-WebDriver is an API for webUi automation testing
=======================================================
Project Setup for Selenium
=======================
1.Using Java project
2.Maven Project

Java Project
===========================
1.create a new Java Project
2.Download selenium jar from selenium.dev
3.right click on project-->build path--->configure build path 
--->libraries-->class path--->add external libraries

Maven Project
====================
Build Management+Project Management Tool

POM.xml file
========================
Project object model this is configuration file for maven Project

1.Dependecy
====================
2.Plugins


<project>

<dependencies>

<dependency>selenium-java</dependency>

</dependencies>



</project>

